  "key_findings": [
    "Pretraining improves DP-GCN accuracy by 3-5% absolute across different privacy budgets",
    "Encoder+classifier transfer works best, suggesting both components benefit from pretraining",
    "Benefits observed at both low (\u03b5\u22483.9) and moderate (\u03b5\u22485-7) privacy budgets",
    "Pretrained model starts at ~30% accuracy vs ~3% for random initialization",
    "Improvements are consistent across different hyperparameters"
