  "conclusion": "MLP pretraining on node features provides a strong initialization for DP-GCN, consistently improving test accuracy by 3-5% at matched privacy budgets. The best result achieved 57.97% test accuracy at \u03b5=7.32, compared to 54.55% for baseline - representing a significant improvement in the privacy-utility tradeoff."
